num2words
=========
 Python3 script for converting integers to spoken English words.

REQUIREMENTS
============
 -python3

USAGE
=====
 - As script
  ---------
   * Type 'python3 num2words.py [integer]' in terminal then <enter>.(Example 'python3 num2words.py 12334563)
   * You can make a script executable then run  './num2words.py 120000'.(on UNIX platforms)
   * You can pass multiple integers separated by whitespace.( Example 'python3 num2words.py 123456 2346 74331 ')

 - As python module
   ----------------
    >>> from num2words import Number
    >>> my_number = Number(1234) # You may use any number
    >>> my_number.convert_to_words()

